PDJ is a browser extension that can help front-end developers easily view the complete dependency relationship of npm packages. It has the following advantages:

1. 🚀 Improved development efficiency
2. 🌟 Display npm package detailed information
3. 💡 Provide convenient way, support Side Panel
4. 🔍 Support search npm package name
